text: Shree Sankhar Mohami Secondary Schoolhttp://so.famedpages.com/www/Shree+sankhar+mohami is a government school situated at Mohami, Sankhar VDC-4, Syangja District, Gandaki Zone, Nepal. It was founded in 1958 AD. This school has been running from class 1 to class 10. This school has been providing education to more than 400 students of Sankhar VDC. ==Magazine== * Golden Jubilee is published in 2010. ==See also== * List of schools in Nepal * School Leaving Certificate (Nepal) ==References== Category:Schools in Nepal
